text: Nicholas Morgan is a former male athlete who competed for England. ==Athletics career== He represented England in the shot put at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games in Cardiff, Wales. He was a member of the Surrey County Athletic Association. ==References== Category:English male shot putters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games Category:Possibly living people Category:Year of birth missing
